<section id="shadows" class="pl-section o-container">
  <h2 class="pl-heading">Shadows</h2>
  <p class="pl-description">Elevation tokens for layering and depth. All shadows use the navy brand colour at low opacity for warmth.</p>

  <div class="pl-specimen--cream pl-specimen">
