  <h3 class="pl-subheading">o-container</h3>
  <p>Centres content with max-width and inline padding. Variants: <code>--sm</code>, <code>--md</code>, <code>--lg</code>, <code>--xl</code> (default), <code>--max</code>.</p>

  <h3 class="pl-subheading">o-grid</h3>
  <p class="pl-label">Fixed columns: o-grid--2, o-grid--3, o-grid--4</p>
  <div class="pl-specimen">
    <div class="o-grid o-grid--3 pl-grid-demo">
      <div>Column 1</div>
      <div>Column 2</div>
      <div>Column 3</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="pl-label">Auto-fit responsive: o-grid--auto</p>
  <div class="pl-specimen">
    <div class="o-grid o-grid--auto pl-grid-demo">
      <div>Auto 1</div>
      <div>Auto 2</div>
      <div>Auto 3</div>
      <div>Auto 4</div>
      <div>Auto 5</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="pl-subheading">o-stack</h3>
  <p>Adds vertical rhythm between child elements. Variants: <code>--sm</code>, <code>--lg</code>, <code>--xl</code>.</p>
  <div class="pl-specimen">
    <div class="o-stack pl-grid-demo">
      <div>Stack item 1</div>
      <div>Stack item 2</div>
      <div>Stack item 3</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="pl-subheading">o-cluster</h3>
  <p>Wrapping horizontal items with consistent gap.</p>
  <div class="pl-specimen">
    <div class="o-cluster">
      <span class="c-tag c-tag--default">Tag One</span>
      <span class="c-tag c-tag--primary">Tag Two</span>
      <span class="c-tag c-tag--secondary">Tag Three</span>
      <span class="c-tag c-tag--default">Tag Four</span>
      <span class="c-tag c-tag--default">Tag Five</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="pl-subheading">o-sidebar</h3>
  <p>Content + sidebar layout that collapses on narrow screens.</p>
  <div class="pl-specimen">
    <div class="o-sidebar pl-grid-demo">
      <div>Sidebar (min 20rem)</div>
      <div>Main content area (grows to fill)</div>
